<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto my-12 px-4 pb-24 font-sans text-stone-800">
  <div class="animate-fade-in-up text-center mb-16" style="animation-delay: 0.1s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-black bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl py-4 px-8 tracking-widest mt-4 inline-block">
      自炊save の使い方
    </h1>
    <p class="text-stone-400 font-medium mt-2">賢く自炊して、お得に楽しもう！</p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-24">
    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10" 
        style="animation-delay: 0.3s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/guide_1.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">1</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">コンビニ商品と比較する</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          投稿画面で、作りたい料理に近いコンビニ商品を選びましょう。<br>自動的に価格が表示され、自炊との差額がリアルタイムで計算されます！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10"
        style="animation-delay: 1.0s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/guide_2.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4 text-right md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">材料とグラムを入れるだけ</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          使った材料と重さを入力すると、自動でコストを算出。「目安表」を使えば、計りがなくてもざっくり計算できます！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10"
        style="animation-delay: 1.2s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/guide_3.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">3</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
        <div class="inline-block bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 text-[10px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest">Achievement</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">「作った！」ボタンをクリック</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          自炊したレシピの「作った！」ボタンをクリックして、節約金額と自炊回数を記録しましょう。<br><br>
          レシピの詳細画面にあるコピーボタンを使えば、自分なりのアレンジレシピも簡単に作れます！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10"
        style="animation-delay: 1.4s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/guide_4.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">4</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4 text-right md:text-left">
        <div class="inline-block bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 text-[10px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest">Summary</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">節約の成果をチェック！</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          プロフィール画面では、「作ったボタン」を押したレシピの「合計節約金額」と「自炊回数」が集計されます。<br><br>
          「これだけお得になった！」「頑張って自炊できている！」というのが一目でわかるので、楽しく自炊を続けられます！</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="animate-fade-in-up mt-24 text-center" style="animation-delay: 1.1s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
    <%= link_to "さっそく作ってみる", new_recipe_path, class: "inline-block bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white font-black px-12 py-5 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl shadow-orange-200 transition-all active:scale-95 text-xl" %>
  </div>
</div>